    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――リズノワのCM撮影から数日経ったある日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1533.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様で～す。お仕事の調子はどうですか～？",
      "startTime": 3.1666666109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。仕事は……まぁいつも通りだな\nこころはどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 13.7666666984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ハード過ぎる現場の合間に顔を出してあげたんですよ～\nどうですか？　かわゆい顔を見て癒されますか～？",
      "startTime": 19.8414513667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだなー。こころのおかげで凄く癒されたぞー\nさーて、残りの仕事も頑張るか……",
      "startTime": 29.5000000317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "対応が雑！　アイドルのマネージャーたるもの\nもっと言葉選びに力を入れて下さい！",
      "startTime": 36.0678744316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんごめん、ちょうど大事なメールが届いて……\nお……こころ、一つ仕事が決まったぞ",
      "startTime": 43.3000000317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事？　私にですか？",
      "startTime": 47.7405894993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "この間リズノワで東京シーサイドのCMを撮影しただろ\nあの時のプロデューサーから連絡があってな",
      "startTime": 54.5333333651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "プールの宣伝用動画を新たに撮らせてもらえないか……\nと依頼を受けたんだ。撮影は来週なんだが……",
      "startTime": 61.6333333651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ～！　楽しそうじゃないですか！\n……って、あれ？",
      "startTime": 69.1333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "来週って確か……莉央さんと葵さんは\n地方でお仕事がありましたよね？",
      "startTime": 73.6666641552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだよ。だから参加出来てもこころと愛の二人\nだけになるって伝えていたんだが、今返事があってな",
      "startTime": 80.5578805617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "「仲のいい二人で元気にはっちゃけてほしいです！」\nと乗り気になってくれているんだ",
      "startTime": 88.5333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "この間の撮影ではスポンサーとプロデューサーにだいぶ\n振り回されましたけど、今度は大丈夫ですよね……？",
      "startTime": 94.4666641552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "安心してくれ、きちんと釘を刺しておいたよ\n現場には俺も同行するから、何かあったら言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 103.8333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "出来るマネージャーは違いますね～。分かりました\n出演します！　愛ちゃんへの連絡はこれからですか？",
      "startTime": 111.8666641552,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7433.335844799998,
          "startTime": 119.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ちょうど今から連絡しようと思って……って\nんん？　こころ、何をしてるんだ？",
      "startTime": 120.5314619034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、もしもし？　愛ちゃんですか～？　たった今\n{user}さんからお仕事の話が――",
      "startTime": 127.9333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "……と、いうことなんです\nだから、こころと一緒にPR動画を撮りましょう！",
      "startTime": 134.7333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "……むむ？　なーんで躊躇してるの？\nこういう時こそ元気を出さないと！",
      "startTime": 142.1666641552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "二人で出演するって伝えるから！　いいね、愛！\nそれじゃあ！",
      "startTime": 148.9999974886,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2350.0025113999927,
          "startTime": 151.35
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ええと、愛は本当に大丈夫なのか？\nなんだか渋っていたような……",
      "startTime": 155.1999974886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "最近うだうだ悩んでるようだったので\nそのせいだと思います",
      "startTime": 160.3774222646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ。ちゃーんと気持ちを切り替えてもらって\n最高のPR動画にしちゃいますから！",
      "startTime": 166.2933721579,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4944.442244599997,
          "startTime": 171.2378144025
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――PR動画撮影当日",
      "startTime": 170.0044861554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい{user}さん！\nどうですかこの神々しいまでの可愛らしさは！",
      "startTime": 175.0999974886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともよく似合ってるよ",
      "startTime": 179.8053199529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "今日はオフ感を大事にするために\nこころ達のスマホで自撮りするんでしたよね",
      "startTime": 184.9999974886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。こころは撮影に、私物の道具を\n使いたいと言っていたけど、ちゃんと持って来たか？",
      "startTime": 191.5333308219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあもうバッチリですよ！　自撮り棒に加えて\nプールや海で遊び倒すために用意していた道具の数々",
      "startTime": 199.066659069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "今日の撮影で存分に使っちゃいますよ～！",
      "startTime": 203.2467659394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "楽しむのはいいけど\nあくまで仕事で来てるのを忘れないようにな？",
      "startTime": 208.766659069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
